if you guys are wondering about the comment the girl made ok her dick being sucked — i haven’t seen the raws, but i’m sure it’s a simple translation error. in japanese, personal pronouns aren’t used very often since they’re usually implied, so the japanese sentence would probably technically translate to something along the lines of “dick felt good to suck/be sucked”, which could be interpreted in a lot of different ways. because of context, she’s most definitely not saying what the translator put — instead, my best guess is that it’s something like either “if felt good to suck his dick” or the awkward-sounding (in english) “his dick being sucked felt good”. i’m just guessing here though, so don’t take my word for it.
